# Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?

Breakout

## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")

A game in which the goal is to break all of the bricks at the top using a ball controlled by a paddle. 

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?

My game will be created using Pygame. It will include three basic elements, the ball, which moves on its own, the paddle, which is controlled by the player, and the bricks at the top that are meant to be broken. When the player breaks all of the bricks, the game is won, but if the ball falls below the paddle, a life is lost. There will be three lives given to the player each round. When all three lives are lost, the player will be prompted to play again. There may also be powerups or obstacles added to the game as added elements, or levels that increase in diffculty when the player breaks all the bricks.  

